description: Hotel Rating Microservices consist of end to end fully  independent services.

name: banking-system-microservices-with-kafka
description: A simple banking system microservices project using Apache Kafka, for learning purposes.

This project demonstrates how to build a scalable, modular application that can handle common banking operations. It uses Spring Boot, Apache CXF, Docker, and Maven.

name: KubeCMS
description: An optimistic attempt to implement a Content Management System in a truly Microservices Architecture inside a Kubernetes cluster.

description: This project is built using the latest version of Spring Boot and demonstrates a microservices architecture for a financial application. The system is composed of several distinct services, each responsible for a specific functionality within the application. The services interact with each other to provide a seamless user experience
